HOUSE BILL NO. HB0003
Animal abuse-predatory animals.
Sponsored by: Joint Travel, Recreation, Wildlife & Cultural
Resources Interim Committee
A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to crimes and offenses; providing for a new
2 criminal offense of cruelty to animals; increasing the
3 maximum fine for a misdemeanor first offense cruelty to
4 animals conviction; providing for the suspension of hunting
5 privileges for a cruelty to animals conviction as
6 specified; authorizing game and fish law enforcement to
7 enforce the criminal provisions of cruelty to animals as
8 specified; specifying applicability; and providing for an
9 effective date.
10
11 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
12
13 Section 1. W.S. 6-3-1002 by creating a new subsection
14 (b), 6-3-1004(a) and by creating a new subsection (c),
